I get that some of you are into getting poor service for kicks. And you love how obnoxious the wait staff is and you just love the paper hats that degrade you.

It was so awkward. Two of the girls in our party were into it and the rest of us were just scared to ask for extra napkins. I wouldn't have minded that much except that food is horrible and overpriced. The whole time I just wished I was at the Burger Bar.